{"tid":1218930,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"認真 星期日之前先按兵不動","createTime":"2019-06-13T17:09:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T17:43:58.000Z","uid":172797,"like":130,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"739a9ada35bd4fe399abc5412c7657ada32f58c2","tid":1218930,"uid":172797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:09:51.000Z","msg":"林奠係on9 但佢唔係弱智，如果唔係一早開會硬推左，洗乜9做專訪流馬尿搏民意同不同延期啊？我地嬴既唔係佔幾條街，沖幾多次，而係<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">民意！民意！民意！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n任何既示威/衝擊/不合作運動都係建基於民意基礎先有攻擊力。政府呢家就係企圖沖淡件事＋觀察民意。<br />\n<br />\n唔好理今個星期日係咪好日子，既然民陣號召左，取消/改日子都會影響士氣，我地就要哂佢冷，全部人上街！<br />\n<br />\n多謝狗隻助攻，政府係輿論戰係處於下風，但佢一直等緊反攻既藉口。<br />\n<br />\n勇武派辛苦你地了，請多多休息，等和理非全面進場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後都係果句，兄弟爬山，星期日前既活動不建議但絕對支持</span></span>"},{"pid":"017e58427f5c2026f30331024383f27426cb01ac","tid":1218930,"uid":213969,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:13:20.000Z","msg":"星期日前唔發夢住<br />\n去金鐘睇下風景算啦"},{"pid":"2a67ade3144570bdda66955a0bc428fb4460eca1","tid":1218930,"uid":172797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:13:48.000Z","msg":"推 俾大家睇"},{"pid":"758eafe3b7232989696d1047657ba2060a633ecb","tid":1218930,"uid":7501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:14:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd75954006ca554d6ddba687f96a1bf807e0a93b","tid":1218930,"uid":172797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:14:28.000Z","msg":"推 俾大家睇"},{"pid":"2d7454b45f222a94568ec9bf1c93add4b43cd7d6","tid":1218930,"uid":172797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:14:38.000Z","msg":"推 俾大家睇"},{"pid":"ba6f6a495e3ec3668adfee0b311fb35b527f295c","tid":1218930,"uid":259901,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:14:38.000Z","msg":"聽日訓晏D，唔洗晨早流流去遊鐵河啦"},{"pid":"3913339f3698aa8abc32d474e7194060a13bb2a1","t